Has everything i need in a calculator. Very intuitive and the display is quite beautiful. Way better than the stock android calculator. Highly recommended.
Sick af
replyContent: Fully hektik

content: This app is an absolute pleasure to us, while I still prefer the tactile elements of a real calculator Natural Scientific emulates perfect the functionality of such devices so it's perfect for when your on the go. It's has a clean layout and intuitive interface makes it a pleasure to use. Count me a happy customer! :)
replyContent: Glad to see you liked it! Hopefully one day we can completely replace physical calculators ;)

content: Very good! I hope this app gets more functions, like a complete scientific calculator. Keep improving.
replyContent: Definitely will do, this is just the start :)

content: I haven't found a calculator with this level of intuitiveness.
replyContent: Glad you found it useful!

content: Gorgeous and easy to use. Suggestions: Show a history of calculations that scroll up as you go. That way the Ans is easier to use. Like on a TI-83. Also, while I like the clearing animation, I wish it were faster. While I like the beauty of the app, I'm here to be productive and I don't want it to slow me down. I would prefer no animation.
replyContent: Hi there, we're implementing a history at the moment and it'll be out in a couple of weeks. As for the clearing animation, that's a valid concern - we'll be adding an option to disable the ripple soon. But please do note, you can begin typing even before the ripple has cleared. The animation is more visual, the input is cleared when you press AC.

content: Looks amazing and works well
replyContent: Hey Daniel, it's been updated substantially since you first downloaded it so go check it out again :)

content: Found this app from reddit! Been using it for a day now, and it's great for students!
replyContent: Thanks for trying out our app, we hope you loved it!

content: Very easy to use. Lovely themes. No complaints. Love that it can easily do fractions.
replyContent: We were inspired by the material design and animations of the stock calculator, but ultimately it was too limited in functionality. Glad you liked it!

content: No question about it.
replyContent: It's the best, but that won't mean we'll rest on our laurels like the top calculator apps on the store today. We'll be continually updating it to make it even better into the future.

content: I love the materialistic design in this app. It flows together smoothly. Having a theme in the app is great! I love to switch up the style every once in a while. I definitely recommend this app to anyone interested in engineering, maths, or science related fields! Well deserved 5 stars!
replyContent: Themes really liven up the app, we're glad you like it! Calculators don't have to be drab and boring ;)

content: I attend university and this app is phenomenal with university level calculus. Fantastic app that's easily the most intuitive of all the calculator apps. Definitely easier to use than my actual graphing calculator. Keep up the great work! Devs like you guys are hard to come by. Let's hope that more app devs have this attitude and devotion to making a great app that works for the user, and not just to make money without providing adequate support, or considering the feedback of the users. Thanks!
replyContent: Thank you so much! That was really heartfelt. It's absolutely fantastic to hear that you're finding our calculator so useful in its current state - I think you'll be even more pleasantly surprised in the future when we roll out more updates!

content: Great calc app.
replyContent: The two golden words, thanks for your review :)

content: After 4 years of using RealCalc, I finally found something to switch to.  Nice clean interface, looks great has all the functions I need.
replyContent: I used RealCalc 4 years ago when I was studying for my finals and while it was good for the time, Android has moved on, while RealCalc has stagnated. Good to hear you liked it!

content: Easily the simplest to use, but with great functionality. My go-to from now on!

content: Best looking scientific calculator and functions perfectly.

content: This app is everything I had hoped for when I bought my electric eel - sleek, efficient, functional and stylish. While there are many things I regret in my life - e.g. purchasing an electric eel - this is certainly not one of them. When I first opened this app, I was shocked (in a different way than an electric eel owner and unintentional breeder is used to). How could such a magnificent app pass by this stagnant app store which such little acclaim? This thought sparked my review - 10/10 would recommend.
replyContent: Yes, we'd also liken our calculator app to your electric eel. Thanks for your masterfully metaphorical review!

content: This is by far the greatest calculator I have ever used.

content: Probably the easiest to use scientific calculator app right now, material design eye candy is a bonus !!
